{"tid":222103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖）香港Butterface大賽","createTime":"2017-04-29T09:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T09:10:34.000Z","uid":85910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8682dac011d24165672a402306e0a519a7bd6b79","tid":222103,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"Butterface: (But-her-face)<br />\nTo call a woman a &quot;butter face&quot; is to say her body is very <span style=\"color: violet;\">sexy</span> but her face is <span style=\"color: green;\">ugly</span>.<br />\n<br />\n外國代表完美示範：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.bannedinhollywood.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/great_body_05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannedinhollywood.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2009%2F10%2Fgreat_body_05.jpg&h=a7d35a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.provedplusprobable.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/butterface.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.provedplusprobable.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F07%2Fbutterface.jpg&h=e2ea0ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=butterface&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwi94tukocnTAhWEerwKHUhmCy4Q_AUICigB&amp;biw=1440&amp;bih=732#imgrc=ZDaJql7lxJN26M:\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dbutterface%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Disch%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwi94tukocnTAhWEerwKHUhmCy4Q_AUICigB%26biw%3D1440%26bih%3D732%23imgrc%3DZDaJql7lxJN26M%3A&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hITCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2554ed22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=butterface&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwi94tukocnTAhWEerwKHUhmCy4Q_AUICigB&amp;biw=1440&amp;bih=732#imgrc=ZDaJql7lxJN26M:</a><br />\n<br />\n香港代表，我先：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20120909/photo/0909-00470-052b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20120909%2Fphoto%2F0909-00470-052b6.jpg&h=d3681e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20160703/s00009/1467533845603_FF58BC053B3EB3E1ED3D778F07674C23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20160703%2Fs00009%2F1467533845603_FF58BC053B3EB3E1ED3D778F07674C23.jpg&h=51fdf0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/s640x640/sh0.08/e35/c0.134.1080.1080/13534328_622848987884236_695289472_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fs640x640%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fc0.134.1080.1080%2F13534328_622848987884236_695289472_n.jpg&h=51c046f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳庭欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Butterface計分方法：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">樣貌分（0至10) 減 身材分（0至10)</span><br />\n0分＝樣靚身材正(10-10 =0)/冇樣冇身材(0-0 =0)（不計入圍）<br />\n10分＝樣靚樣冇身材(10-0 =10)（不計入圍）<br />\n-10分＝冇樣有身材(0-10 =-10 = 終極butterface<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n負分數開始被列為butterface<br />\n<br />\n以陳庭欣為例：<br />\n樣：4分<br />\n身材：9分<br />\n<br />\n4-9= -5分<br />\n<br />\n陳庭欣樣唔算極差 但以港姐冠軍黎講就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因此樣有4分<br />\n副Body波、腳、腰都達到十分高既水平<br />\n美中不足下椿肉地唔夠<br />\n少少地扣1分<br />\n<br />\n-5分成績不俗 各巴打請出招（參賽請附圖，否則取消資格）"}]}